Klinsmann Ready for Action on Sunday
LONDON , February 27 ( Xinhua ) -- Germany captain Juergen Klinsmann has recovered from a broken jaw and will return to English premier league action on Sunday , local reports said here on Friday .
The striker has been included in Tottenham 's squad for their relegation battle at home with Bolton Wanderers .
The German star , who broke his jaw in a F.A .
Cup tie against Barnsley in early February , was initially thought to be sidelined for the rest of the season and possibly miss the World Cup .
But the injury has proved to be less serious than expected .
